Package: orientchessr
Title: Use R to Play Chinese Chess
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Ho",
           family = "Chia",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "r08h41005@ntu.edu.tw")
Description: Chinese chess is hard to explain or understand by 
    reading the chess records without visualizing the records. 
    Render the chess rocords in pictures or gif that makes you easier 
    to learn and share with others. 
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
